stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Published: publish()/broadcast()/request() → MessagePublished
  Published --> Expired: now ≥ expiresAt (TTL) → MessageExpired
  Published --> Delivering: select target(s)
  Delivering --> Delivered: handler ack (resolves) → MessageDelivered
  Delivering --> Retrying: handler nack (throws), retries remain → MessageRetried
  Retrying --> Delivering: after delayMs
  Retrying --> DeadLettered: retries exhausted → DeadLettered
  Delivered --> [*]
  Expired --> [*]
  DeadLettered --> [*]

  note right of Delivering
    Delivery model chosen by the caller:
    • pub/sub  → every distinct group
    • p2p      → one member per shared group (round-robin)
    • broadcast→ every subscriber
    • request  → resolves on reply(), else RequestTimeoutError
    A failing subscriber never blocks the others.
  end note
